<br>
When my ranger hunted forest giants in WW, he SOLOED them with no problem at level 30. He was modestly equipped, but not great. Far from great, looking back. /sigh. He would be able to take out the full 3 pop giant hut without needing to med, just heal a little.<br>
<br>
Before giants maybe try brutes by the Dalnir zoneline in Warsliks Woods as well. It's a bit of a walk, but you're always guaranteed single pulls, decent cash from gem drops, and there's a zoneline right there in the event you get in trouble.<br>
<br>
~Alyindar Courwood, Elven Ranger and Treehugger Extraordinaire <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub51.ezboard.com/feternalhonourfrm1.showPrevMessage?topicID=130.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub51.ezboard.com/feternalhonourfrm1.showNextMessage?topicID=130.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/feternalhonourfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=130.topic&index=0><img src=http://eqjunk.netfirms.com/ezboard/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/feternalhonourfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=130.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/feternalhonourfrm1.threadControl?topicID=130.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/space/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/feternalhonourfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=130.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub51.ezboard.com/feternalhonourfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=130.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub51.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="eternalhonourfrm1">General<option value="eternalhonourfrm3">Open Raids<option value="eternalhonourfrm4">Membership Applications<option value="eternalhonourfrm7">Jokes/Funny Stories<option value="eternalhonourfrm15">Member Listing<option val